            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Hmm.. We always can do this:\n\n```c\nstatic int parser_gc(lua_State *L)\n{\n  TSParser **ud = luaL_checkudata(L, 1, TS_META_PARSER);\n  if (*ud) {\n    logger_gc(ts_parser_logger(*ud));\n    ts_parser_delete(*ud);\n    *ud = NULL;\n  }\n  return 0;\n}\n```\n\nDoes that sound reasonable?",
